Gamesa Advances After Agreement With Chinese Companies, Sales Forecast

-- B y   T o d d   W h i t e   a n d   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-04-13T07:20:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-13/gamesa-advances-after-agreement-with-chinese-companies-sales-forecast.html
Gamesa Corp. Tecnologica SA climbed
as much as 3.1 percent in  Madrid  after saying it signed
memoranda of understanding with three Chinese energy companies
including China Longyuan Power Group to supply them with 900
megawatts of its  wind turbines . The shares rose as high as 7.20
euros and traded at 7.18 euros, up 2.8 percent, at 9:18 a.m.
local time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Todd White at 
 twhite2@bloomberg.net  